WEBVTT

01:42.840 --> 01:45.000
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL
HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

02:21.440 --> 02:22.520
Here, let me help you.

04:07.120 --> 04:08.160
Okay.

04:08.240 --> 04:09.120
Sang…

04:18.040 --> 04:19.079
I guess

04:19.160 --> 04:20.560
I'll take this one with me.

04:20.640 --> 04:21.880
Okay.

04:21.959 --> 04:23.240
Perfect. One for each of us.

04:25.720 --> 04:27.120
Why don't we get something to eat?

04:30.760 --> 04:31.960
It's late.

04:32.040 --> 04:33.960
Why don't we go back to campus?

04:35.480 --> 04:36.960
Okay, let's go.

04:37.560 --> 04:38.480
Okay.

04:43.400 --> 04:44.560
I had fun today.

04:46.040 --> 04:46.960
Sang Zhi.

04:47.520 --> 04:49.400
Do you want to get dinner at the canteen?

04:50.600 --> 04:52.360
I'll just order takeout.

04:52.440 --> 04:53.320
You're back.

04:54.120 --> 04:55.480
- Hi.
- Come on.

04:56.200 --> 04:58.160
We were just talking
about spending New Year's Eve

04:58.240 --> 04:59.720
at the Central Plaza.

04:59.800 --> 05:02.200
Influencers recommend it.
We can get a lot of nice photos.

05:02.280 --> 05:03.120
Central Plaza?

05:03.200 --> 05:04.480
- Yes.
- It will be crowded.

05:04.560 --> 05:06.320
Right? That's what I told her.

05:06.400 --> 05:07.440
She wouldn't listen.

05:07.520 --> 05:08.400
Then…

05:12.800 --> 05:14.200
Why don't you join us, Jiang Ming?

05:14.280 --> 05:15.240
It's New Year's Eve.

05:15.320 --> 05:16.280
The more, the merrier.

05:16.360 --> 05:17.240
Right?

05:17.320 --> 05:18.160
Sure.

05:23.040 --> 05:24.560
I have to go back to my dorm.

05:24.640 --> 05:25.480
You guys carry on.

05:25.560 --> 05:26.400
Bye.

05:30.520 --> 05:31.640
Did he win this for you

05:31.720 --> 05:32.720
from the claw machine?

05:33.280 --> 05:34.600
I got this myself.

05:34.680 --> 05:36.560
Well, what do you think about Jiang Ming?

05:39.400 --> 05:40.360
I think he's a good guy.

05:40.440 --> 05:41.560
He's handsome and nice.

05:41.640 --> 05:43.480
That brother of yours
can't be much better.

05:52.040 --> 05:54.080
Sangsang, I'll ask you one last time.

05:54.160 --> 05:55.720
Won't you spend New Year's Eve with us?

05:55.800 --> 05:57.280
I am sure.

05:57.360 --> 05:58.480
It's cold outside.

05:58.560 --> 05:59.960
But if you--

06:00.040 --> 06:01.600
No more buts.

06:01.680 --> 06:03.160
Sangsang already said no.

06:03.240 --> 06:05.200
Besides, the place will be crowded.

06:05.280 --> 06:07.440
We might see more heads than fireworks.

06:07.520 --> 06:08.800
That's right. Weiwei.

06:08.880 --> 06:10.240
You go ahead and enjoy yourself.

06:10.800 --> 06:12.200
- Let's go.
- All right.

06:30.600 --> 06:32.000
Wangwang.

06:34.920 --> 06:36.920
Are you trying to compete with me?

06:37.720 --> 06:39.520
This won't do. I have to change my outfit.

06:39.600 --> 06:41.880
No, Ning Wei. No need to change.

06:41.960 --> 06:43.840
You are the prettiest.

06:43.920 --> 06:45.760
You are the second prettiest.

06:45.840 --> 06:46.760
Okay. Great. Let's go.

06:46.840 --> 06:49.040
I think it's too short. I'll go change.

06:49.120 --> 06:50.200
It's not short. It's fine.

06:50.280 --> 06:52.320
It's perfect for this occasion. Let's go.

06:52.400 --> 06:54.280
- Let me get my coat.
- Okay.

06:54.360 --> 06:55.640
Hurry.

06:55.720 --> 06:56.800
- Sangsang.
- Let's go.

06:56.880 --> 06:58.320
Remember to eat.

06:58.400 --> 06:59.800
I know. I'll order takeout.

07:00.320 --> 07:01.640
We'll bring back tasty treats too.

07:02.200 --> 07:03.640
Don't miss us too much.

07:04.160 --> 07:05.000
Sangsang.

07:05.080 --> 07:06.560
- Happy New Year!
- Happy New Year!

07:07.360 --> 07:08.800
- We're off.
- Bye.

07:08.880 --> 07:10.600
- Bye.
- Bye. Remember to eat.

07:12.240 --> 07:13.240
Be careful.

07:13.320 --> 07:14.560
- Okay.
- There are a lot of people.

07:14.640 --> 07:15.840
Okay. Bye.

07:34.040 --> 07:34.880
There you are.

07:36.040 --> 07:37.600
I want to give Weiwei a surprise,

07:38.480 --> 07:40.360
but I don't want her to yell at me again.

07:41.120 --> 07:42.920
Why? Just tell her.

07:43.000 --> 07:44.280
Last time, I ordered hot pot

07:44.360 --> 07:45.800
and she yelled at me for three days.

07:46.280 --> 07:48.040
It's fine. There's always a next time.

07:48.960 --> 07:50.800
- Hello.
- Hi.

07:51.720 --> 07:52.880
Where's Weiwei?

07:52.960 --> 07:53.880
Hey!

07:57.120 --> 07:59.200
- Hi.
- Hi.

07:59.280 --> 08:00.960
You're not wearing glasses today.

08:02.360 --> 08:03.320
What do you think?

08:03.400 --> 08:05.280
Isn't she pretty without her glasses?

08:05.840 --> 08:07.040
Yes.

08:08.280 --> 08:10.360
Be more confident. Stand straight.

08:10.440 --> 08:11.920
Stop teasing me.

08:12.000 --> 08:14.200
Enough. It will be really crowded today.

08:14.280 --> 08:15.800
We won't get a spot if we don't go now.

08:15.880 --> 08:17.120
- Let's go.
- Where's Sang Zhi?

08:17.200 --> 08:18.400
Didn't she come with you guys?

08:18.480 --> 08:19.400
No.

08:19.480 --> 08:20.520
- She's not going.
- No.

08:21.080 --> 08:22.240
Is she not coming?

08:22.320 --> 08:23.920
Sangsang has never liked crowds.

08:24.000 --> 08:25.840
She'll stay in and watch anime. Right?

08:25.920 --> 08:27.200
- Yes.
- Yes.

08:27.280 --> 08:28.600
So let's go.

08:28.680 --> 08:30.320
- We're going to be late!
- That's right.

08:30.400 --> 08:31.240
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

08:31.320 --> 08:32.600
- Come on, Chen Qiang.
- Let's go.

08:32.679 --> 08:34.559
Come on. Jiang Ming, let's go!

08:36.360 --> 08:37.480
Okay, I'm the fifth wheel.

09:11.680 --> 09:12.600
Jiaxu.

09:12.680 --> 09:13.880
What are you doing?

09:15.480 --> 09:16.360
Nothing.

09:17.640 --> 09:19.640
There's a company dinner tonight.

09:19.720 --> 09:21.240
I can bring my family.

09:21.320 --> 09:22.560
I'll bring you.

09:22.640 --> 09:24.000
I'm not your family.

09:25.600 --> 09:26.960
I'll pass.

09:27.040 --> 09:28.760
I'm about to eat the takeout I ordered.

09:28.840 --> 09:30.360
Takeouts on New Year's Eve?

09:32.200 --> 09:33.800
If you don't like crowds,

09:34.280 --> 09:35.560
the two of us can have dinner.

09:39.840 --> 09:41.160
I don't feel like going out.

09:42.840 --> 09:44.360
You still owe me a meal.

09:44.440 --> 09:45.480
Are you trying to back out?

09:47.360 --> 09:49.280
I'll make a reservation right now.

09:49.360 --> 09:51.000
You get ready to come out.

09:51.840 --> 09:53.560
- I--
- I'm almost at your university.

09:58.240 --> 09:59.400
I'll get changed.

10:01.040 --> 10:02.720
Good. I'll call you when I get there.

10:14.320 --> 10:16.600
CHAPTER 11, MOVED

10:16.680 --> 10:18.520
IF THIS IS LOVE

10:31.280 --> 10:32.120
Try this.

10:36.520 --> 10:38.880
Why didn't you go out with your roommates?

10:38.960 --> 10:40.080
Do you guys not get along?

10:41.640 --> 10:42.560
No.

10:43.840 --> 10:45.760
We get along just fine.

10:45.840 --> 10:48.160
But they're going to the Central Plaza

10:48.240 --> 10:49.880
for the New Year's Eve countdown.

10:49.960 --> 10:50.960
It's too crowded for me.

10:51.960 --> 10:53.280
And Yihe is too cold.

10:53.360 --> 10:54.320
I didn't want to go out.

10:55.080 --> 10:56.680
But you said yes the minute I asked.

11:02.160 --> 11:03.320
That's because…

11:04.480 --> 11:06.840
That's because I owe you a meal.

11:06.920 --> 11:08.680
If I didn't come,

11:08.760 --> 11:10.160
you would think I'm trying

11:10.240 --> 11:11.800
to get out of treating you.

11:13.960 --> 11:15.920
I was just kidding about that.

11:22.360 --> 11:23.280
By the way,

11:24.480 --> 11:25.760
I didn't mean

11:25.840 --> 11:27.720
to tease you at the hospital.

11:33.920 --> 11:34.880
So

11:36.040 --> 11:39.200
I want to formally apologize to you today.

11:47.320 --> 11:48.760
You don't have to do that.

11:48.840 --> 11:50.600
It's not a big deal.

11:50.680 --> 11:52.480
Besides, that was a long time ago.

11:55.000 --> 11:56.000
All right.

11:57.120 --> 11:58.120
Eat more.

11:58.880 --> 12:00.040
It's my treat.

12:00.120 --> 12:01.240
Consider it my apology.

12:03.040 --> 12:04.600
Didn't we agree that it is my treat?

12:05.320 --> 12:07.080
I owe you a meal anyway.

12:07.640 --> 12:08.880
What do you mean?

12:09.600 --> 12:12.240
Are you saying
that we don't have to meet again

12:12.320 --> 12:13.800
after this meal?

12:18.280 --> 12:20.520
Have some sympathy
for this lonely old man.

12:21.080 --> 12:22.840
You won't even have a meal
with your brother.

12:26.840 --> 12:27.840
Jiaxu.

12:29.840 --> 12:31.000
Start digging in.

12:31.080 --> 12:32.800
You're really talkative today.

12:34.640 --> 12:37.160
It's not every day
that I get to have a meal with you.

12:37.240 --> 12:38.520
So what if I want to talk more?

12:40.440 --> 12:41.720
Let's talk about you.

12:43.000 --> 12:45.640
How are your classes?

12:46.400 --> 12:48.000
Are you interested in them?

12:50.560 --> 12:51.760
The professor says

12:52.280 --> 12:54.360
that freshmen don't have
many major courses.

12:55.160 --> 12:57.160
But we will have many as sophomores.

12:59.760 --> 13:00.960
Lame.

13:01.520 --> 13:02.360
Let's sit here.

13:02.440 --> 13:03.360
Okay, let's sit here.

13:10.640 --> 13:12.480
That's what my professor said.

13:17.320 --> 13:18.560
Why won't you answer my calls?

13:26.160 --> 13:27.480
I've told you.

13:28.200 --> 13:30.080
We don't need to stay in touch anymore.

13:32.640 --> 13:33.840
Jiang Ying!

13:38.640 --> 13:39.600
Who are you?

13:39.680 --> 13:40.920
What's wrong with you?

13:41.000 --> 13:42.200
And what's wrong with you?

13:42.280 --> 13:43.320
It's none of your business!

13:43.400 --> 13:44.640
Do you know why I did that?

13:44.720 --> 13:46.720
I don't care why.

13:46.800 --> 13:48.960
Listen, if you had assaulted him,

13:49.040 --> 13:50.360
I would've returned the favor.

13:51.960 --> 13:53.120
Jiang Ying!

13:58.720 --> 13:59.920
What do you want, Jiang Ying?

14:01.040 --> 14:02.880
Who is she, Duan Jiaxu?

14:03.360 --> 14:04.600
Jiang Ying, don't! Let's go.

14:04.680 --> 14:05.760
Sorry, miss. Please leave.

14:05.840 --> 14:07.000
Do you think you're in the clear?

14:07.080 --> 14:09.760
Listen, you owe me
for the rest of your life!

14:10.320 --> 14:11.800
- Please leave.
- Let's go.

14:11.880 --> 14:13.680
- You think you don't owe me anymore?
- Leave!

14:13.760 --> 14:14.800
- Duan Jiaxu!
- Get out!

14:14.880 --> 14:16.640
I will never let you off!

14:16.720 --> 14:18.000
Let me go!

14:19.040 --> 14:19.920
Jia…

14:21.280 --> 14:22.360
Are you okay?

14:24.200 --> 14:25.360
Let's leave, Jiaxu.

14:49.960 --> 14:51.760
It's cold. Put your coat on.

15:25.680 --> 15:26.760
So, Jiaxu.

15:27.560 --> 15:28.920
Who is that woman?

15:32.160 --> 15:33.160
Someone unimportant.

15:40.960 --> 15:42.040
To be precise,

15:43.680 --> 15:45.560
I guess she's my dad's former creditor.

15:48.280 --> 15:49.360
Wait!

15:49.880 --> 15:50.800
I'm going inside.

15:54.320 --> 15:55.720
I ran into her once.

15:56.440 --> 15:57.520
Did you?

15:58.440 --> 15:59.640
When you were hospitalized,

15:59.720 --> 16:01.280
I went to get your things at your place.

16:02.120 --> 16:03.600
We walked past each other.

16:04.160 --> 16:05.280
Did she do anything to you?

16:12.320 --> 16:13.600
So I guess

16:14.520 --> 16:15.920
she was there

16:17.200 --> 16:18.360
to see you.

16:20.160 --> 16:22.720
Does this happen every time she sees you?

16:25.400 --> 16:26.680
No.

16:39.760 --> 16:40.640
Jiaxu.

16:42.160 --> 16:43.440
As you said,

16:44.400 --> 16:46.040
she's your dad's former creditor.

16:47.120 --> 16:48.680
So it has nothing to do with you.

16:49.480 --> 16:51.200
You shouldn't let her bully you.

16:53.960 --> 16:54.880
I don't…

16:56.200 --> 16:57.880
There's no way she can bully me.

17:04.400 --> 17:05.240
What's the matter?

17:16.160 --> 17:17.160
I'm fine.

17:17.680 --> 17:18.720
I don't need…

17:37.560 --> 17:38.480
Does it hurt?

17:41.200 --> 17:42.080
No.

18:05.680 --> 18:06.880
I forgot to say this earlier.

18:12.000 --> 18:13.200
Thank you, Sang Zhi.

19:12.920 --> 19:14.640
I wish that all bad things

19:14.720 --> 19:16.640
will stay away from Jiaxu.

19:18.240 --> 19:19.880
I wish that someone could be with him.

19:20.680 --> 19:21.680
I wish

19:22.560 --> 19:23.680
that person is me.

19:33.600 --> 19:34.840
Aren't you going to make a wish?

19:35.320 --> 19:36.560
It's this year's first snowfall.

19:38.000 --> 19:39.360
Yihe doesn't get snow often.

19:40.280 --> 19:41.480
The last time it snowed

19:42.400 --> 19:43.920
was when I was in tenth grade.

19:46.280 --> 19:47.720
I guess

19:48.280 --> 19:49.440
I'm quite lucky.

19:50.680 --> 19:51.760
I'm lucky too.

19:52.800 --> 19:55.160
I get to see the snowfall with you.

20:02.880 --> 20:04.440
A wish at the first snowfall

20:04.520 --> 20:05.760
is said to come true.

20:16.880 --> 20:17.760
I wish

20:18.520 --> 20:21.600
Sang Zhi will always be happy and healthy,

20:22.480 --> 20:23.440
and so will I.

20:31.680 --> 20:33.120
What was your wish?

20:35.360 --> 20:36.920
It won't come true if I say it out loud.

20:38.360 --> 20:39.480
What did you wish for?

20:42.040 --> 20:43.880
It won't come true if I say it out loud.

21:14.120 --> 21:15.400
I wish…

21:18.280 --> 21:20.440
No, I can't let you guys hear it.

21:33.360 --> 21:34.720
What did you guys wish for?

21:35.600 --> 21:37.000
Of course,

21:37.520 --> 21:38.840
for us to be together forever.

21:41.640 --> 21:43.400
Goodness, I wish

21:43.480 --> 21:44.600
that I never have to listen

21:44.680 --> 21:46.000
to Ning Wei's mushy lines anymore.

21:46.080 --> 21:47.520
If you're so jealous,

21:48.880 --> 21:50.640
you should get a boyfriend too.

21:50.720 --> 21:51.560
That's right.

21:54.400 --> 21:55.440
Wangwang.

21:55.520 --> 21:56.680
What did you wish for?

21:57.400 --> 21:58.280
Me?

21:59.160 --> 22:00.200
I…

22:00.280 --> 22:03.000
There isn't anything I really want.

22:03.080 --> 22:04.880
There isn't?

22:04.960 --> 22:06.960
This is the first snow in Yihe in years.

22:07.040 --> 22:08.560
But you don't have any wishes!

22:09.160 --> 22:10.520
You watch romance dramas, right?

22:11.200 --> 22:12.760
They always say

22:12.840 --> 22:14.160
that wishes at the first snowfall

22:14.240 --> 22:15.160
will come true.

22:16.960 --> 22:17.840
Really?

22:17.920 --> 22:18.880
Of course.

22:18.960 --> 22:20.360
That's nonsense.

22:20.440 --> 22:22.480
The first snow calls
for beer and barbecue.

22:22.560 --> 22:23.800
Don't stand around. Come on.

22:24.400 --> 22:25.640
Good grief!

22:25.720 --> 22:27.320
She doesn't have a single romantic bone.

22:27.400 --> 22:29.280
You're single by your own virtue, Yu Xin.

22:29.360 --> 22:32.200
- Let's do it. Who will do it?
- Look, my boyfriend barbecues for me.

22:32.280 --> 22:33.400
Please!

22:33.480 --> 22:35.120
Let this year be over already.

22:43.440 --> 22:44.520
Jiang Ming.

22:46.320 --> 22:47.480
What did you wish for?

22:47.560 --> 22:48.680
Me?

22:51.520 --> 22:52.640
It's all right.

22:52.720 --> 22:54.240
You don't have to tell me

22:54.320 --> 22:55.240
if you don't want to.

22:55.840 --> 22:56.680
It's no big deal.

22:57.560 --> 22:59.360
I wished that the person I like

22:59.440 --> 23:00.560
would make a wish today

23:01.320 --> 23:03.120
and that her wish would come true.

23:08.240 --> 23:10.720
The person you like is really lucky.

23:13.440 --> 23:14.360
The meat is done!

23:14.440 --> 23:15.640
Do you guys want some or not?

23:16.200 --> 23:17.960
- Coming!
- Hurry!

23:18.040 --> 23:19.200
Let's head over.

23:42.280 --> 23:44.280
Jiaxu, I'm sorry.

23:44.360 --> 23:45.600
I was too impulsive today.

23:45.680 --> 23:47.160
Tell your friend that I apologize.

23:47.240 --> 23:48.120
I'm sorry.

23:49.880 --> 23:50.920
What's the point of this?

23:51.480 --> 23:53.360
Sorry, I won't do it again.

23:54.040 --> 23:55.120
Please move.

23:55.200 --> 23:57.160
I said I'm sorry, Duan Jiaxu!

23:57.240 --> 23:58.480
I already told you

23:58.960 --> 24:00.440
not to contact me anymore.

24:01.840 --> 24:03.920
So you're cutting me off
after paying off the debt?

24:04.000 --> 24:05.280
What gives?

24:05.360 --> 24:06.920
Don't you know that you owe me,

24:07.000 --> 24:08.240
Duan Jiaxu?

24:08.320 --> 24:09.720
What do I owe you? Tell me.

24:09.800 --> 24:11.280
Your dad killed my dad!

24:11.360 --> 24:12.280
You owe me!

24:12.360 --> 24:14.000
You know what you owe me!

24:17.880 --> 24:19.400
You just owe me.

24:20.920 --> 24:22.960
I've repaid what I should.

24:24.240 --> 24:26.280
My dad paid the price too.

24:27.560 --> 24:29.000
I don't owe you anything else.

24:29.760 --> 24:31.440
Duan Jiaxu!

24:34.120 --> 24:35.800
Duan Jiaxu!

24:35.880 --> 24:38.960
Don't forget what your mom promised us!

24:39.560 --> 24:42.600
She said you would always take care of me!

25:35.840 --> 25:37.720
Leave! You're not welcome here!

25:37.800 --> 25:38.640
Sorry, Mrs. Jiang!

25:38.720 --> 25:40.120
Get out. Leave.

25:40.200 --> 25:41.080
Leave now!

25:41.160 --> 25:42.720
- I'm sorry, Mrs. Jiang!
- Get out!

25:42.800 --> 25:44.160
- Mrs. Jiang.
- Why are you here?

25:44.240 --> 25:45.320
I'm sorry.

25:45.400 --> 25:47.480
He's dead! What's the use of these things?

25:47.560 --> 25:50.200
You destroyed my sister's family!

25:50.280 --> 25:51.480
Sorry.

25:51.560 --> 25:53.240
It's our fault.

25:53.320 --> 25:54.840
What is the use of saying sorry?

25:54.920 --> 25:57.560
Will that bring Xiaoying's dad back?

25:57.640 --> 26:00.040
What will Xiaoying and her mom do now?

26:03.480 --> 26:04.840
I want my dad.

26:07.480 --> 26:09.680
I just want my dad.

26:11.320 --> 26:12.240
Xiaoying.

26:12.960 --> 26:14.120
I'm sorry, Xiaoying!

26:14.200 --> 26:15.360
Mom!

26:15.440 --> 26:16.680
Mom, what are you doing?

26:16.760 --> 26:18.400
We've done you wrong.

26:21.120 --> 26:22.040
Rest assured.

26:23.080 --> 26:25.120
- Mom.
- We will take responsibility.

26:25.200 --> 26:27.520
We will pay the compensation
decided by the court.

26:27.600 --> 26:28.960
Even if we have to sell our house,

26:29.040 --> 26:29.880
take out a loan,

26:29.960 --> 26:31.120
or borrow money,

26:31.200 --> 26:32.560
no matter what,

26:33.120 --> 26:36.640
we will pay you on time.

26:37.360 --> 26:39.200
My son and I

26:40.160 --> 26:41.640
will look after you and your daughter

26:42.120 --> 26:44.120
for life as well.

26:44.760 --> 26:48.400
SORRY

27:27.320 --> 27:28.560
Jiang Ying.

27:29.160 --> 27:31.160
You've been away from school for a while.

27:31.720 --> 27:33.480
You can ask me if you need help.

27:39.800 --> 27:41.880
Did you know that Jiang Ying's dad died?

27:42.520 --> 27:43.480
I've heard.

27:44.200 --> 27:46.840
Apparently, Duan Jiaxu's dad ran him over.

27:46.920 --> 27:48.720
- Seriously?
- Yes.

27:48.800 --> 27:50.040
What are you guys talking about?

27:51.600 --> 27:52.680
Duan Jiaxu's dad ran over

27:52.760 --> 27:54.200
and killed Jiang Ying's dad.

27:54.280 --> 27:55.600
He was still alive at the time.

27:56.120 --> 27:57.720
He died after Jiaxu's dad fled the scene.

27:58.360 --> 28:00.600
Doesn't that make him a murderer's son?

28:00.680 --> 28:01.560
That's right.

28:10.280 --> 28:12.320
Doesn't that make him a murderer's son?

28:13.520 --> 28:15.280
How can he still come to school?

28:15.360 --> 28:16.360
If I were him,

28:16.440 --> 28:17.800
I wouldn't dare to show my face.

28:57.280 --> 28:58.400
I'm sorry, Mom.

29:02.440 --> 29:03.480
I can't do it.

29:18.800 --> 29:20.040
Jiaxu.

29:20.120 --> 29:21.720
As you said,

29:22.280 --> 29:24.160
she's your dad's former creditor.

29:25.280 --> 29:26.920
So it has nothing to do with you.

29:27.680 --> 29:29.200
You shouldn't let her bully you.

29:33.040 --> 29:33.880
Sang Zhi,

29:34.800 --> 29:35.800
thank you.

31:16.440 --> 31:19.520
SANG ZHI

31:19.600 --> 31:21.960
Happy New Year, Jiaxu.

31:22.040 --> 31:23.280
May you be happy every day.

31:26.240 --> 31:27.160
BROTHER NO. 2

31:27.240 --> 31:28.200
Happy New Year.

31:35.160 --> 31:36.360
I'm watching the fireworks.

31:37.160 --> 31:38.400
What about you?

31:45.560 --> 31:47.520
BROTHER NO. 2

31:47.600 --> 31:48.880
Me too.

31:49.600 --> 31:50.640
They're beautiful.

32:13.720 --> 32:14.760
EDIT CONTACT DETAILS

32:14.840 --> 32:15.840
SANG ZHI

32:17.800 --> 32:21.120
ZHIZHI

32:21.200 --> 32:22.360
So, Jiaxu.

32:23.400 --> 32:24.720
Who is that woman?

32:26.240 --> 32:27.560
What do I owe you? Tell me.

32:27.640 --> 32:29.080
Your dad killed my dad!

32:29.160 --> 32:30.120
You owe me!

32:30.200 --> 32:32.080
You know what you owe me!

32:34.040 --> 32:36.240
Your voice sounds young,

32:36.320 --> 32:37.920
but you can't fool anyone.

32:38.000 --> 32:39.560
You're not young anymore.

32:39.640 --> 32:41.120
He is not my partner.

32:42.200 --> 32:43.640
He is too old.

32:43.720 --> 32:45.160
He is old enough to be my dad.

32:50.840 --> 32:52.640
SAVE CHANGES?

32:52.720 --> 32:53.600
SAVE

33:26.120 --> 33:27.720
DON'T SIT FOR TOO LONG

33:27.800 --> 33:29.360
GET UP AND MOVE, BYE

33:40.840 --> 33:41.760
DON'T SIT FOR TOO LONG,
GET UP AND MOVE, BYE

33:53.480 --> 33:54.840
Let me tell you guys something.

33:54.920 --> 33:56.520
I am getting married!

33:57.080 --> 33:59.080
I'm getting hitched!

33:59.160 --> 34:01.080
QIAN FEI

34:01.160 --> 34:02.440
I bet you're pissed!

34:03.880 --> 34:04.760
What's up?

34:04.840 --> 34:06.040
Are you all asleep?

34:06.560 --> 34:08.440
Why are you ignoring me
when I'm so excited?

34:09.800 --> 34:10.800
Not yet.

34:10.880 --> 34:17.480
DUAN JIAXU

34:20.159 --> 34:21.000
Well?

34:21.080 --> 34:21.960
You're still up?

34:22.040 --> 34:23.760
What? Did you miss me?

34:24.800 --> 34:25.679
I'm hanging up.

34:25.760 --> 34:27.000
Don't!

34:27.080 --> 34:28.920
If you're still up, chat with me.

34:29.000 --> 34:30.320
Guess what? I proposed today.

34:30.400 --> 34:31.520
Do you know how I proposed?

34:31.600 --> 34:33.159
When I saw her home today,

34:33.239 --> 34:34.639
I told her I was thirsty

34:34.719 --> 34:36.560
and to get me a bottle of water
from the trunk,

34:36.639 --> 34:37.880
so she did.

34:37.960 --> 34:39.080
The minute she opened it,

34:39.159 --> 34:40.320
she saw it filled with roses.

34:40.400 --> 34:41.960
I went up to her and said,

34:42.040 --> 34:43.560
"Will you be my wife?"

34:43.639 --> 34:44.679
Guess what she said?

34:44.760 --> 34:47.040
She said, "Won't that make me Mrs. Qian?"

34:47.120 --> 34:48.520
Isn't she cute?

34:49.639 --> 34:51.120
Nice.

34:52.360 --> 34:54.199
But I'm sad to hear

34:54.280 --> 34:55.679
that you're getting married.

34:56.360 --> 34:59.000
You always said
you were going to stay single with me.

34:59.080 --> 35:01.280
I only said that to make you feel better.

35:01.360 --> 35:02.440
Did you take it seriously?

35:05.320 --> 35:06.160
All right.

35:06.680 --> 35:08.160
Congratulations, buddy.

35:10.240 --> 35:12.400
Enough about me. What about you?

35:12.480 --> 35:15.320
Didn't you say
you were going on a blind date?

35:15.400 --> 35:16.560
Did you?

35:16.640 --> 35:18.680
What blind date? No way.

35:20.360 --> 35:21.880
Has anyone caught your eye?

35:21.960 --> 35:23.360
You must have feelings for someone.

35:36.000 --> 35:37.000
Jiaxu.

35:37.080 --> 35:38.920
I think I've caught a trace of something

35:39.000 --> 35:41.240
from your few seconds of silence.

35:41.320 --> 35:42.560
What's going on?

35:42.640 --> 35:44.080
Who is it?

35:44.160 --> 35:45.440
What do you…

35:45.520 --> 35:46.560
Tell me.

35:46.640 --> 35:47.880
Have you calmed down yet?

35:47.960 --> 35:48.960
Hurry up and go to sleep.

35:49.040 --> 35:50.360
You're about to be a married man.

35:50.440 --> 35:52.120
- No, tell me who it is.
- I'm hanging up.

36:02.880 --> 36:04.720
What am I thinking?

36:10.400 --> 36:15.680
NO MILK OR EGGS

36:17.200 --> 36:18.680
Kiddo.

36:21.520 --> 36:24.680
CLEAR AMBITIONS, LEARNING,
SELF-CULTIVATION, AND DILIGENCE

36:25.600 --> 36:27.560
Weiwei, what did you buy?

36:27.640 --> 36:28.640
That's a huge box.

36:28.720 --> 36:29.800
Two pairs of shoes.

36:29.880 --> 36:31.080
They were on sale.

36:31.160 --> 36:32.400
I couldn't help it.

36:32.480 --> 36:34.000
- Jiaxu.
- What did you buy?

36:34.080 --> 36:35.640
- I have something for you.
- Stationery.

36:35.720 --> 36:36.640
Stationery?

36:36.720 --> 36:38.320
- I'll come to your office.
- How boring!

36:38.400 --> 36:39.640
Why buy stationery?

36:42.120 --> 36:43.560
- Weiwei.
- What did you buy, Sangsang?

36:43.640 --> 36:44.520
I bought…

36:45.560 --> 36:46.440
Chen Qiang.

36:46.520 --> 36:48.320
- Do you need help? I'll get that.
- I've got it.

36:48.400 --> 36:49.880
You have a class later. I'll manage.

36:49.960 --> 36:51.080
It's fine.

36:51.160 --> 36:52.400
Let's go eat after my class.

36:52.480 --> 36:53.560
Sure.

36:55.680 --> 36:56.720
Sang Zhi.

36:56.800 --> 36:58.680
You weren't there on New Year's Eve.

36:58.760 --> 37:00.280
Are you free this weekend?

37:00.360 --> 37:01.840
Let's decompress.

37:03.680 --> 37:04.960
But exams are around the corner.

37:05.040 --> 37:06.960
Maybe after we finish our exams.

37:07.040 --> 37:08.320
Exams?

37:09.120 --> 37:10.200
That's right.

37:10.280 --> 37:12.040
I have a friend who just opened up a bar.

37:12.120 --> 37:15.240
Why don't we all go there to celebrate
after our exams?

37:15.320 --> 37:17.560
Let's talk about that after our exams.

37:17.640 --> 37:18.840
What should we eat for dinner?

37:19.560 --> 37:20.640
That's right!

37:20.720 --> 37:22.480
I heard a new place opened up.

37:22.560 --> 37:23.400
Let's try it.

37:23.480 --> 37:24.440
I heard it's good.

37:24.520 --> 37:25.600
Tonight?

37:25.680 --> 37:27.520
You guys try it first.

37:27.600 --> 37:28.960
I'll pass tonight.

37:29.040 --> 37:30.240
Where are you going?

37:30.920 --> 37:33.560
I'm going to deliver a peephole camera

37:33.640 --> 37:34.480
to my relative.

37:35.800 --> 37:36.720
All right.

37:36.800 --> 37:38.280
I'll be leaving now.

37:38.360 --> 37:39.520
- Bye.
- Bye.

37:40.080 --> 37:41.600
Be careful. Come back early.

37:41.680 --> 37:42.720
Stay safe.

37:43.800 --> 37:45.520
For NPC feedback,

37:45.600 --> 37:47.480
if we program it this way,

37:47.560 --> 37:49.120
every time the player runs into them,

37:49.200 --> 37:51.840
it will trigger many event detections.

37:52.440 --> 37:54.440
If so, phones with lower specs

37:54.520 --> 37:55.640
won't be able to process it

37:55.720 --> 37:56.960
and will lag.

37:57.040 --> 37:58.560
Can I write it with C instead?

37:59.440 --> 38:01.280
Stop it with the C.

38:01.360 --> 38:03.120
JAVA is the best.

38:05.000 --> 38:07.400
It's fine. It's not a huge issue.

38:07.480 --> 38:08.720
We've had a long day.

38:08.800 --> 38:09.880
Let's end this meeting here.

38:09.960 --> 38:11.480
- Good work, Jiaxu.
- Good work.

38:12.080 --> 38:13.000
Let's go.

38:13.800 --> 38:15.720
It's tough.

38:21.200 --> 38:22.280
Clean up after yourself.

38:33.360 --> 38:35.840
ARE YOU BUSY? I CAN LEAVE IT
AT YOUR BUILDING'S RECEPTION DESK.

38:39.720 --> 38:41.000
Where are you?

38:44.960 --> 38:45.880
What should we do?

38:45.960 --> 38:47.080
Go downstairs and stop her.

38:47.160 --> 38:48.680
- Okay.
- Xiaoduan.

38:49.480 --> 38:50.360
Come here.

38:52.920 --> 38:53.760
What's the matter?

38:53.840 --> 38:55.920
Jiang Ying is making a scene
again downstairs.

38:56.000 --> 38:57.640
I asked security to stop her.

38:57.720 --> 38:58.760
It should be fine.

39:26.600 --> 39:27.720
You cannot enter.

39:27.800 --> 39:29.120
Hold on. Wait at the entrance.

39:29.200 --> 39:31.080
- Listen! I'm looking for Duan Jiaxu!
- Wait.

39:31.160 --> 39:33.080
- He works here.
- I know what you're saying, miss.

39:33.160 --> 39:34.280
But you cannot enter yet.

39:34.360 --> 39:35.840
- I'm his friend.
- I'll help you.

39:35.920 --> 39:37.080
We'll let him know now.

39:37.160 --> 39:39.200
- If he gives permission--
- I just need to talk to him.

39:39.280 --> 39:41.040
Please wait here. Calm down.

39:41.120 --> 39:42.240
My colleague has--

39:42.320 --> 39:44.040
- Wait. You can't go inside.
- It's important!

39:44.120 --> 39:46.160
You can't enter. I know what you mean.

39:46.240 --> 39:47.920
- Please!
- Miss, you can't just enter.

39:48.000 --> 39:50.080
- Wait. You can't enter.
- I just need to say something.

39:50.160 --> 39:51.800
We're working. You cannot just go inside.

39:51.880 --> 39:52.840
- Please.
- Jiaxu.

39:52.920 --> 39:54.000
You cannot go inside.

39:54.640 --> 39:55.560
I'm his friend.

39:55.640 --> 39:57.240
My superior said we can't let you in.

39:57.320 --> 39:58.360
- Come.
- He must be upstairs.

39:58.440 --> 39:59.520
Mr. Duan isn't inside.

40:00.880 --> 40:02.320
Don't push me!

40:06.320 --> 40:07.480
Why didn't you pick up?

40:09.160 --> 40:11.040
Sorry, my phone ran out of battery.

40:11.120 --> 40:12.520
I forgot to charge it last night.

40:12.600 --> 40:14.040
Why didn't you tell me you were here?

40:15.240 --> 40:16.320
I did.

40:17.080 --> 40:18.960
I sent you a message. Didn't you see it?

40:19.040 --> 40:20.360
I was busy. I missed it.

40:21.080 --> 40:22.160
It's okay.

40:22.720 --> 40:23.560
Sang Zhi.

40:24.320 --> 40:26.960
Don't come straight to my office
or my place anymore.

40:27.040 --> 40:28.800
If you do, let me know beforehand, okay?

40:35.280 --> 40:36.600
Have you eaten?

40:44.840 --> 40:46.200
I wanted to give you this.

40:48.400 --> 40:49.520
A peephole camera.

40:50.320 --> 40:52.680
That woman keeps harassing you.

40:53.840 --> 40:55.920
You can install this on your door.

40:56.000 --> 40:57.320
It can connect to your phone.

40:57.400 --> 40:58.640
It's a smart camera.

40:58.720 --> 41:01.600
You can use it to call the police too.

41:01.680 --> 41:03.840
It will come in handy.

41:04.600 --> 41:06.160
That's all.

41:06.240 --> 41:07.400
Thank you.

41:08.000 --> 41:09.520
Go back to work.

41:09.600 --> 41:10.720
I'm going back to class.

42:55.760 --> 42:58.160
That woman keeps harassing you.

42:58.240 --> 42:59.080
SMART DOORBELL

42:59.160 --> 43:00.840
You can install this on your door.

43:01.680 --> 43:03.840
It will come in handy.
